      <h3>About Gyalpozhing College of Information Technology</h3>
      <p>
        Gyalpozhing College of Information Technology (GCIT) is a specialized constituent college under the Royal University of Bhutan established in 2017.
        It aims to provide quality IT education to prepare students with industry-relevant skills in emerging technologies.
      </p>
      <p>
        GCIT offers undergraduate programs focusing on Artificial Intelligence, Blockchain, Cybersecurity, Full Stack Development, and Interactive Design. The college is equipped with modern IT labs, a library, and supports innovative learning.
      </p>
      <p>
        The campus is located in Chamjekha, Thimphu, offering a conducive environment for students to develop both academically and personally.
      </p>
