    <h3>GCIT Admission Instructions & Eligibility</h3>
    <p><strong>Before applying</strong>, please read the instructions carefully and ensure you meet the admission requirements.</p>

    <h4>Who Can Apply?</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Students who have passed Class XII and meet eligibility criteria.</li>
      <li>Applicants committed to completing a 4-year IT program.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>When to Apply?</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Review programs carefully before applying.</li>
      <li>Apply through the GCIT Admission Portal when ready.</li>
      <li><strong>Last date for online registration: 15 March 2025</strong></li>
      <li>Application final once submitted; program category changes are not allowed.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Application Conditions</h4>
    <p>Choose only <strong>one</strong> program category:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Category A:</strong> AI Development, Blockchain, Cybersecurity.</li>
      <li><strong>Category B:</strong> Full Stack Development, Interactive Design & Development.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Funding Options</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Government Scholarship (Higher-Education Grant)</li>
      <li>Self-Financed</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Ensure accurate personal details and an active contact number to receive your application notification.</p>

